who caused the trouble?

83
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:14,980
Sister,

84
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:17,060
listen to me.

85
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:20,860
You have to fix this problem quickly.

86
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:23,420
