167
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:04,860
-Yes.
-I want my mother.

168
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:05,740
Zhun, let's go.

169
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:08,060
-Mother.
-Zhun.

170
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:11,180
Zhun, let's go.

171
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:13,140
I want my mother.

