223
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:35,140
and plan it for the long term.

224
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,380
Mother,

225
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,860
no worries.

226
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:41,580
I understand.

227
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,180
I can wait.

228
