273
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,860
we can handle it in time.

274
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:42,340
Just rest assured

275
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:45,060
and get ready to become

276
00:12:45,260 --> 00:12:46,900
the Marquis's wife.

277
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,620
